data.description: Nicely updated 3 bedroom, 1 bath home near Wold Lake. Home offers open floor plan with large living room, recently remodeled kitchen, dining room and all 3 bedrooms on one level. Large privacy fenced back yard with patio area and shed for storage. 1 stall garage with dolomite flooring and electric hooked up inside. Amazing landscaping both front and back yards along with underground sprinkler in the back. 1/4 mile from 2 different beaches on Wolf Lake. Oakridge Elementary, middle and high school all within a short distance. A/C installed is 2013, new roof in 2014, well is 8 yrs old, natural gas and city sewer. Schedule your showing today before it's gone! *** Assumable FHA loan at 2.85%!!!
